{"tid":1114491,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講，無論jupas定後門入計，PolyU TSE都係無得輸。（月入80k）","createTime":"2019-04-18T13:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T12:12:02.000Z","uid":3874,"like":11,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44299ee442e668b80d55072908f16cdf66103a93","tid":1114491,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"2月22日，合肥廣場派出所接到報警，報警人稱：其在火車站與地鐵一號線相連的通道內遇到一對母子，以錢包被盜沒錢買車票回家為由向其求助，稱借錢買票回家後將通過微信返還。但微信轉賬給對方後不久，報警人便發現自己的微信號已被對方拉黑，方知自己被騙，遂報警。<br />\n<br />\n  對該案，合肥火車站派出所黨支部高度重視，經過兩日的摸排、追踪、取證，24日下午，警方將正在火車站廣場行騙的兩名違法犯罪嫌疑人抓獲。經查，2人系母子關係，兒​​子今年才15歲。據交代，其二人利用春運及學生返校高潮，以被盜沒錢回家為伎倆，在火車站、汽車站等人員流動密集的場所向過往旅客&ldquo;演戲&rdquo;，騙取對方同情心和金錢。<br />\n<br />\n  根據兩名嫌疑人的交代，他們行騙的對像多挑年輕人和學生下手，利用被騙對象的善良和愛心，以自己無錢買車票回家為由，獲取錢財，金額50、100、200不等，大多數受害人發現被騙後也只自認倒霉，所以才讓他們屢屢得手，所以他們更加的有恃無恐。<br />\n<br />\n  廣場派出所民警在和一受騙的女學生聯繫時，得知其轉給嫌疑人的200元錢是其10天的生活費，而在警方獲取的二人手機裡，當日兩人詐騙總數額已達2000餘元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ah.sina.com.cn/news/s/2019-02-27/detail-ihsxncvf8131435.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fah.sina.com.cn%2Fnews%2Fs%2F2019-02-27%2Fdetail-ihsxncvf8131435.shtml&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=dd241b90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ah.sina.com.cn/news/s/2019-02-27/detail-ihsxncvf8131435.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n只要各位畢業生擁抱大灣區 返去廣州深圳各大高鐵站乞食 月入80k不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗收入之外 TSE嘅同學仔仲可以比年輕女lecturer教3-4個cources<br />\n係各位Engine仔少有接觸到女性嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>認住我 PolyU JS3351 Transportation Systems Engineering</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e8fe1e3d16bfc0d8e1c5608f825f447ea669117b","tid":1114491,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a669da8e713f1c4fc82630c9930a04829f4bf0","tid":1114491,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"收到wind樓g tse grad去起高鐵 fg60k"},{"pid":"da6a12e91222aa11e77b98cd8eadb4961c58abf2","tid":1114491,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fe1e3d16bfc0d8e1c5608f825f447ea669117b","tid":1114491,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"捉緊大灣區嘅機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a966570f27a9663751faa97b2a317bb73eff573c","tid":1114491,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"03a669da8e713f1c4fc82630c9930a04829f4bf0","tid":1114491,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"收到wind樓g tse grad去起高鐵 fg60k"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ec33b84e52ef946709eca13143f3de0a28c42e","tid":1114491,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a966570f27a9663751faa97b2a317bb73eff573c","tid":1114491,"uid":3874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"03a669da8e713f1c4fc82630c9930a04829f4bf0","tid":1114491,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:10:16.000Z","msg":"收到wind樓g tse grad去起高鐵 fg60k"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236d204f4197a63f28d3423c10e26bd0d47f6cb0","tid":1114491,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a966570f27a9663751faa97b2a317bb73eff573c","tid":11144